Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎、怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.92,0:02:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 辛苦你們囉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:54.14,Name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,960)}9's專用FRANXX
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,以人類來說表現算可以了
