Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不會有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不用擔心唷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:26.34,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(923.2,540)}我……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:26.34,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(925.7,540)}我……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,要乖乖等我們回來唷 廣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,等這次作戰結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我會重新教你操縱方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:38.35,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(923.2,540)\1c&H000000&}該何去何從…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.72,0:03:38.35,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(925.7,540)\1c&H000000&}該何去何從…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...大家 要平安回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:45.35,Name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,960)}第六波FRANXX聯合中隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.56,0:03:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,目標為F2地點 全體出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.82,0:04:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就憑你們 連讓我熱身都不夠格!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,無論來多少架都一樣啦
