Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 要上囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,先下一城了 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害...感覺像多了好幾架鶴望蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1362,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也該上場了
