Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那些是?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,第13部隊的孩子們啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,α很中意他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(760,980)}Alpha
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 這就是妳的機體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,蠻可愛的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,還真是多謝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是說 戰況呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然暫時撐住了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但持續這樣下去也不會有結果的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,往那瞧 有看到嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那個巨大窟窿被堅固的圓頂覆蓋著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,唯有從內部下手 我們才有可能破壞掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.00,0:05:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,得從那裡進去嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,青葙和金雀花跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(724,980)}Argentea
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(960,980)}Genista
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,吊蘭負責在後方援護射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(662,980)}Chlorophytum
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:17.24,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(923.2,540)}我，將不復存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:17.24,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(925.7,540)}我，將不復存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,直接用最大火力上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喔喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那些是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,從沒見過那種戰鬥方式...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,第13部隊嗎...一如往常的亂來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣我們就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人 趁這個時候重整態勢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,滿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要上囉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那是...人造建築嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 準備從那裡攻進去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼回事?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.16,0:06:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,叫龍往四周逃竄開來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,自地底確認到瑪格瑪能量活性化反應
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:15.10,Background,,0,0,0,,再次確認震波
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哦哦 原來還藏著這麼一手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:17.54,Background,,0,0,0,,判定為超雷曼級
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:21.24,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}雷曼-布倫不連續面(Lehmann–Bullen discontinuity)，\N地球外核和內核交界。一般在5155km深處，\N由發現者丹麥地震學家英格·雷曼以及紐西蘭數學家\N凱思·艾華·布倫的姓氏共同命名之。
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,超雷曼級...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這可從未聽聞啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,山...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,山動起來了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,第26要塞都市...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.04,0:07:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的都市被...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙打算直接破壞所有要塞都市
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,超雷曼級叫龍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,開始自座標E3移動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有三座要塞都市位於其預測動線上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1376,980)}protocol
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,建立和090的通訊 執行32號協議
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1113,980)}protocol
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,您是說...32號協議嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不 沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.84,0:07:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,CODE:090
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這可是極為光榮的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,超雷曼級叫龍 正筆直朝此處移動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,預估雙方接觸時間為240秒後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去...會直接撞上的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,大事不妙 牠朝著第13都市去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你、你說什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來 該怎麼做呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那些是...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1213,980)\fs40}protocol
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人 執行32號協議
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣 是最好的結果吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.86,0:08:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,第13部隊 之後就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,怎、怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,停...停下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我、我們的都市被...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,大家 快去保護好都市
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,ZERO TWO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:21.44,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-M-GBK\pos(960,584)\1c&H000000&}輪廓 漸漸模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:21.44,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-M-GBK\pos(960,585.5)\1c&H000000&}輪廓 漸漸模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:23.82,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-M-GBK\pos(960,584)}誰能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:23.82,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-M-GBK\pos(960,585.5)}誰能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:25.82,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-M-GBK\pos(960,584)}帶我離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:25.82,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-M-GBK\pos(960,585.5)}帶我離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,快關閉所有閘門
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦這裡被攻陷 就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,正是 當務之急為擊退該架超雷曼級叫龍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:35.82,Background,,0,0,0,,大裂縫那邊將由爸爸們代為管控
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 待在這太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,請盡快返回本部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,廣也是 快回鳥籠去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1105,980)}Mistilteinn
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你不覺得 她遠比人類還來的美麗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不帶一絲雜念的崇高自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,無以復加的孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,早已無異乎於叫龍...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不對! ZERO TWO她才不是叫龍...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.84,0:10:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,原本還想說 這次一定沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真是可憐的丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:03.68,Place,,0,0,0,,{\pos(107,960)}第13要塞都市 內部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,吼 到底還要打倒幾隻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.64,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,別抱怨了 胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我們可是在保護我們的都市啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.86,0:10:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不准叫我胖子!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 再多來幾發剛剛的光束砲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的能量早就不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,而且備用的也都用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,咦~小氣鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,大家得互相合作才行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚哇 超恐怖的 看來她今天心情不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,光想像得和牠為敵就足以讓人不寒而慄了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那種醜陋的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,ZERO TWO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.86,0:10:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,ZERO TWO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那時 妳想說的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.02,0:11:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:06.59,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(923.2,540)}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:06.59,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(925.7,540)}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟在猶豫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:10.09,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(923.2,540)}是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:10.09,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(925.7,540)}是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,被逼到最底了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不能再讓牠們靠近一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,沒彈藥了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,子彈用完的話 就用蠻力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.82,0:11:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,慢...慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.98,0:11:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,混帳 我們怎麼能輸...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這個都市要靠我們守護啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.24,0:11:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 莓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,莓 小心背後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,別分心了 莓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.34,0:11:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,為 為何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼訓練機會出現在這?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗚哇! 那、那是怎樣!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那該不會是...廣?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是從何時開始的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.02,0:12:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不再渴望去了解各式各樣的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那時的我只想知道外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,一心想離開花園而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,以往的我只有孤獨 以及隻身一人帶來的不安作伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.64,0:12:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 當我見到那個當下的妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,認為發現了一起對抗世界的同伴時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:24.71,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-M-GBK\an5\pos(896.533,540)}Z\NE\NR\NO\N\NT\NW\NO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:24.71,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-M-GBK\an5\pos(899.033,540)}Z\NE\NR\NO\N\NT\NW\NO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:27.71,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(923.2,540)}我想讓妳知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:27.71,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(925.7,540)}我想讓妳知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.70,0:12:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我是多麼地高興
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,非妳不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有妳...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有妳的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.82,0:12:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我什麼都做不到!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,廣 為什麼你要跑來這
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,光靠那台訓練機 又打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓你過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:12:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 五郎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒辦法看著廣和ZERO TWO這樣下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 廣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.20,0:13:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你有話非得對她說不可吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,莓 妳帶廣去ZERO TWO那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,妳也很耿耿於懷不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,ZERO TWO的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.98,0:13:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 莓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是一堆麻煩事欸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.36,0:13:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不管男生女生都一樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,要上囉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.26,0:13:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,廣的意識...湧進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:44.26,Background,,0,0,0,,成為我的Darling吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:45.38,Background,,0,0,0,,你表現得很好唷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這些是...什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.38,0:13:46.76,Background,,0,0,0,,輕而易舉 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:47.90,Background,,0,0,0,,想和我一起操縱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:49.38,Background,,0,0,0,,如果是我 能帶Darling離開這裡唷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,廣的...記憶?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.38,0:13:50.72,Background,,0,0,0,,如何 想反悔的話只剩現在了唷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不要...我不想再看了!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.12,Background,,0,0,0,,當然是來擊退怪物的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:53.18,Background,,0,0,0,,你也和其他人一樣 認為我是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:55.26,Background,,0,0,0,,你只不過是我的餌食罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易和廣連結上了 但這樣根本....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:56.66,Background,,0,0,0,,從現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:58.32,Background,,0,0,0,,你就是我的Darling了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:59.09,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,120)\fnFZYaSong-M-GBK\an5\pos(896.533,540)}等\N著\N我\N\NZ\NE\NR\NO\N\NT\NW\NO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:59.09,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,120)\fnFZYaSong-M-GBK\an5\pos(899.033,540)}等\N著\N我\N\NZ\NE\NR\NO\N\NT\NW\NO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:01.09,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,0)\frz270\pos(923.2,540)}…等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:01.09,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(130,0)\frz270\pos(925.7,540)}…等我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.44,0:14:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,根本沒得比嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,滿腦子盡是她的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.72,0:14:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要出發囉 廣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那裝什麼帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:23.83,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-M-GBK\pos(960,584)}人類家家酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:23.83,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-M-GBK\pos(960,585.5)}人類家家酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:26.58,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-M-GBK\pos(960,584)}如今 也 沒必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.58,0:14:26.58,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-M-GBK\pos(960,585.5)}如今 也 沒必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:29.21,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,0)\fnFZYaSong-M-GBK\pos(960,584)}輪廓 逐漸模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:29.21,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,0)\fnFZYaSong-M-GBK\pos(960,585.)}輪廓 逐漸模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:34.80,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-M-GBK\pos(960,584)}我……是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:34.80,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYaSong-M-GBK\pos(960,585.5)}我……是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.48,0:14:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真想...成為人類呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,ZERO TWO!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,莓!? 為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經受夠了...每次都被妳牽著鼻子走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.74,0:14:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,住手 莓!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要是妳...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有出現在這那該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我這就把廣讓給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.96,0:15:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,妳倒是給我...乖乖恢復正常啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是我 ZERO TWO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我來見妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,保護好鶴望蘭!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1055,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很不甘心 但那頭龐然大物...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,只有鶴望蘭能打倒牠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(862,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,數量明顯變少了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,別掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這還是第一次 打倒這麼多架
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 未來 好像有東西掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那是...什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,看起來...很像人類
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,欸!? 別說那種奇怪的話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就、就是啊 怎麼可...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,爆炸?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,第37要塞都市 備份程序已完成98%
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,去吧 從肉體的桎梏中...解放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.24,0:16:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那是怎樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,大、大人們都還在裡面不是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,難道...他們讓都市自爆了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.70,0:16:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,終於開始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,看來爸爸們打算不靠鶴望蘭結束這一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.98,0:16:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1062,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟還得犧牲多少座呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,做到這個份上嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.24,0:16:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,愚蠢至極
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,果然毫無反應嗎 既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.20,0:16:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我得碰妳了 ZERO TWO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,求求妳 讓我再次...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,再次待在妳身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,CODE:016的記憶已更動完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是關於CODE:002
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,有片區塊仍然無法被覆寫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,彷彿受某股強大的力量保護般
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,刪除所有記憶 那只會影響實驗結果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 連續啟動會超過腦部的負荷量...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,CODE:016要如何處置?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.86,0:17:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他回到花園
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然混入了血液的他已經毫無用處
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但做為實驗對象倒還有點意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我深信 一旦忘記...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.00,0:18:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定就再也無法成為人類了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.64,0:18:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,第一個記住的詞彙是...「我」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,接著是 「ZERO TWO」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 第三個是....
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那樣一來 我就是妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,「Darling」了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,「Darling」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.14,0:18:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,直到今天...妳都還記得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊 對你很感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.30,0:18:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,成為我的Darling吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.64,0:18:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,從現在開始 你就是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我的Darling了!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,即使全身傷痕累累
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:18:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,妳仍然一個人...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,挺身對抗著這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:03.61,Style01,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(875.2,540)\1c&H000000&}　我就在這裡。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.27,0:19:03.61,Style02,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(877.7,540)\1c&H000000&}　我就在這裡。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dar...Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,終於見到妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,別、別看我!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.70,0:19:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你不怕我嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我過去...都在利用你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那種事 怎樣都好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可是...可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,還說了Darling你只是餌食
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我也把妳稱作怪物過啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣就...扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯...正因為我是怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以才...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.94,0:19:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好好聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.18,0:19:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我們非找出來不可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,世上一定有著我們能去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕得從此刻開始!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這個世界肯定比我們所想的...還要大上許多!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然那個時候沒能實現...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:19:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但這次...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:20:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們一起邁向外頭的世界吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,ZERO TWO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不會再分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒好嗎 廣!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴望蘭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(960,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那光芒...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,鶴望蘭!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(958,980)}Strelizia
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,ZERO TWO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,ZERO TWO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,能與你相遇真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,ZERO TWO 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,最喜歡妳了!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.42,0:21:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,傻瓜 好歹先切掉通訊嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 傻到不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太好了呢 你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,ZERO TWO 破壞那個圓頂 沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那當然! 只要和Darling在一起的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 我們也動身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.74,0:22:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 要開始囉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.16,0:22:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.68,0:22:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣一來 大裂縫的門就敞開了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,終於 離解放人類之時指日可待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.68,0:22:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,比翼鳥 似乎是這樣稱呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.90,0:22:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那是一種 生來只擁有單側羽翼的鳥類
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.56,0:22:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,雄鳥與雌鳥 如果不並翼而行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.82,0:22:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,便無法翱翔於天空 帶有殘缺的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.60,0:22:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.52,0:22:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.46,0:22:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.42,0:22:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,對於那樣的生存方式
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.10,0:22:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,卻感到 格外地美麗
